      'faq-06-03' : 'So in a nutshell, what is #TraceChain?',
      'faq-06-04' : '#TraceChain is the next generation of Blockchain systems. The solution is based on an autonomous self-studying routing algorythm. It starts its functioning at a speed of 50,000 transactions per second (basic speed of a 100 Mb/s channel) and increases by adding reasonable numbers of high speed channels. These channels form the core of #MetaHash network and make its work stable.',
